---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout lang="en" title="Home" description="First Up Productions. Corporate video and content production for companies. Strategically conceived, cinematically executed.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center bg-brand-black overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-black/40 via-brand-black/60 to-brand-black z-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <!-- Replace with: <video src="/hero-reel.mp4" autoplay muted loop playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover" /> -->
      <!-- Or replace with: <img src="/hero-bg.jpg" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover" /> -->
      <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-dark via-brand-gray to-brand-black opacity-80"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-20 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-heading font-semibold leading-tight mb-6">
        <span class="text-brand-accent"> Effective </span> video production for your company.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-light/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-light leading-relaxed">
        Videos and films, strategically conceived and cinematically produced. For companies and organisations that want a professional presence and real results.
      </p>
      <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- POSITIONIERUNG -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-dark">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-light/80 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        First Up Productions is a video and content studio focused on corporate clients, based in Germany. We combine cinematic craft with a clear understanding of what drives business success. The goal is not just a good video — it is content that strengthens your company in the direction you want, that convinces, and that shapes your professional presence over the long term.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WAS WIR FÜR SIE PRODUZIEREN — Unified offer -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-black">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-4">What we produce for you</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">The right content for your company — everything you need. Strategically conceived, professionally executed.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Intro Box: full-width explanatory card -->
      <div class="mb-6">
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-8 md:p-10 border border-brand-accent/15 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Results that fit your company.</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            The following examples show what we typically produce for our clients. At the same time: every project is developed individually — based on your goals, your needs, and the type of collaboration that makes the most sense for you. We define scope, setup, and outcome together.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-8 border border-white/5 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Brand presence</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">Corporate films, brand films and image videos — films that position your company professionally. For website, campaigns, and your entire corporate communication.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-8 border border-white/5 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Interviews & corporate communication</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">Employees, leaders, clients — professionally captured and shaped so that your voices build trust and your company culture becomes visible.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-8 border border-white/5 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Social media & business content</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">LinkedIn videos, reels, short-form formats — professionally produced and tailored to the channels where your audience actually is.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-8 border border-white/5 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Event & company coverage</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">Conferences, corporate events, trade shows — documented and reusable as content for your ongoing communication.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a href="/en/services" class="btn-outline">Explore services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WAS GUTE VISUELLE KOMMUNIKATION LEISTET -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-dark">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading text-center mb-16">What professional content does for your company</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Clear positioning</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">Professional video content shows what your company stands for. Clear positioning on your website, on social media, and in presentations. Visible, credible, memorable.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Authenticity</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">People trust what they see. A well-produced company film and consistent content build more credibility than any bullet-point presentation.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Versatile by design</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">A single shoot day can produce formats for website, LinkedIn, recruiting, internal communication, and social media. Content that works across multiple channels.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">A professional corporate presence</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">The quality of your visual communication speaks for your company. Cinematic corporate content positions you where you belong.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROZESS / SO LÄUFT DIE ZUSAMMENARBEIT -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-black">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-4">How we work together.</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-muted max-w-xl mx-auto">Clear processes and personal support. That is how content gets made that lands.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-4">01</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading mb-3">Conversation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">We talk through your goal, your audience, and the context. This is where the foundation for everything else is built.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-4">02</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading mb-3">Concept</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">We develop a concept that fits your goal. Everything is thought through in terms of content, visuals, and logistics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-4">03</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading mb-3">Production</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">On the shoot day we handle everything: direction, camera, sound, light. Efficient, with focus on what matters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-4">04</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading mb-3">Delivery</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">Editing, color grading, sound design, and so on. The finished result in every format you need.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WARUM FIRST UP -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-dark">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading text-center mb-16">Why First Up Productions?</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Cinematic standard</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">Our background is in film. Directing, storytelling, and visual narrative are second nature. You feel it in every project: stronger visual language, more deliberate staging, more depth.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">A lasting point of contact</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">You speak directly with the people executing your project. Short paths, clear communication.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">A strategic approach</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">We think along from the very beginning. Where will the content be used? Who is it for? What should it trigger? That is how we make content that actually works — and not just looks good.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Flexibly plannable</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">Whether single project or ongoing partnership: we are a reliable partner that thinks ahead and adapts to your needs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FÜR WEN DAS SINNVOLL IST -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-black">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading text-center mb-12">Who this is for</h2>
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-4">
        {[
          'Companies that want to shape their communication professionally and visibly',
          'Companies looking for an external production partner for their video work',
          'Companies that want to strengthen employer branding, recruiting, and culture visually',
          'Organisations that need high-quality content for their channels on a regular basis',
          'Leadership teams that want to raise their corporate presence to a new level',
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 text-brand-light/70">
            <span class="text-brand-accent mt-1 shrink-0">—</span>
            <p>{item}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LAUFENDE ZUSAMMENARBEIT TEASER -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-dark border-y border-white/5">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-6">Also as an ongoing partnership.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-light/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        Do you need not just a single video but regular professional content for your company — for social media, recruiting, internal communication, or your website? Then let's talk about an ongoing collaboration. Fully plannable, reliable, and at your level.
      </p>
      <a href="/en/services" class="btn-outline">Learn more</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STIMMEN -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-black">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-center mb-12">What clients say</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <blockquote class="bg-brand-dark p-8 border border-white/5">
          <p class="text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">&ldquo;Professional, thoughtful, and completely uncomplicated to work with. He understood what we wanted to communicate and delivered a result that exceeded our expectations.&rdquo;</p>
          <footer class="text-sm text-brand-accent">— Managing director, mid-sized company</footer>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote class="bg-brand-dark p-8 border border-white/5">
          <p class="text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">&ldquo;From concept to finished film, everything was clearly structured. No agency overhead — just one point of contact who really understood our corporate communication.&rdquo;</p>
          <footer class="text-sm text-brand-accent">— Head of marketing, technology company</footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABSCHLUSS CTA -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-black">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-heading mb-6">Let's talk about your project.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-light/60 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
        No commitment, personal, direct. Tell us what you have in mind and we'll tell you honestly how we can help.
      </p>
      <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
